title: Ep - 132 - RONNIE KARAM REVIEWS 90 DAY FIANCÉ PREMIERE
description:
Ronnie Karam from Watch What Crappens podcast helps Kate review the season premiere of 90 Day Fiancé, which offers a unique look into the world of international dating and matrimony. The stakes are incredibly high as these couples are forced to make a life-altering decision: get married or send their international mate home, and Ronnie and Kate can’t stop laughing as they review all the couples featured this season.


Reality Life with Kate Casey
